1. *Ubilo* ih je nepoznato oružje. (Unknown weapon *killed* them.)
2. Ubila me je njena lepota. (Her beauty *killed* me.)
3. Ne znam ko je *ubio* vreme u ovom kafiću. (I don't know who *killed* time in this cafe.)
4. Vozač je *ubio* brzinu na autoputu. (The driver *killed* speed on the highway.)
5. Uvreda *ubija* više nego mač. (An insult *kills* more than a sword.)
6. *Ubij* dosadu ovog vikenda izlaskom sa prijateljima. (*Kill* boredom this weekend by going out with friends.)
7. Ona ne želi da *ubija* životinje i postala je vegetarijanka. (She doesn't want to *kill* animals and became a vegetarian.)
8. *Ubijaju* me bolovi u leđima. (Back pains are *killing* me.)
9. Ljubomora može *ubiti* ljubav. (Jealousy can *kill* love.)
10. Nisam mogao da spavam, komarac me je *ubijao*. (I couldn't sleep, a mosquito was *killing* me.)